data.description: Come check out the newly painted two-story house!  Here's your chance to get a 5-bedroom, 3-bath, 3 car garage with plenty of storage, and workspace in Temecula.  The main floor features ceramic tile throughout, a spacious on-suite bedroom/den with double doors, a full wall-to-wall triple closet, full bathroom with stand-up shower, laundry room, with a convenient laundry chute, (Maytag washer and dryer included) extra storage closet and cabinets, a living room, family room, a formal dining area, with wall-to-wall custom-built shelving, and an elegant chandelier.  The kitchen features granite counter tops, newly painted cabinets, gas range with built in microwave vent, dishwasher, and plenty of cabinet space.  The kitchen also has a reverse osmosis drinking water purification at the sink and has a hook up for your fridge as well.     The second floor has a spacious on-suite master bedroom, with double vanity, walk-in closet, stand-up shower, and large soaking tub.  The other three upstairs bedrooms all have ceiling fans, and chrome trimmed mirrored closet doors.  One of the upstairs bedrooms could also double as an office if needed with extra shelving, and lighting built right in!    Other features are:  Almost new HVAC system, water softener, a tankless instant hot water heater, whole house fan, and solar!     The home is located in a nice neighborhood near the Redhawk waterfall, and golf course, and is close to schools, parks, restaurants, shopping, services, and public transportation.     The yard is a unique gardener's paradise full of fruit trees!  With rocks in the front yard, and wood chips in the back, the yard boasts a Concord Muscadine grape vines, 10 mixed green and purple fig trees, 4 Kiowa blackberry bushes, 2 pomegranate trees, 6 very productive Black Mulberry trees, 3 Passion Fruit Vines, 1 Dragon Fruit cactus, 2 Guava trees, 1 Santa Rosa plum tree, 1 Cumquat, 1 Loquat, 1 Star Cherry bush, 2 varieties of Gooseberry, a Raspberry bush, several Japanese Chocolate vines, Asparagus, Horseradish, Sorrell, 2 Lemon trees, 2 small avocado trees, and a Feijoa (Pineapple Guava) bush.
